*Story*
once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on the banks of a river
in the same forest there lived a crocidle and his wife
one day the crocidle came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree
the kindharted  monkey offreed him some fuits
the crocidle came back the next day for more fruits
as he loved them as days passed by
the crocidle and the monkey became good frends  